# 1 Saatte 1 Kitap - Expo Audio Book App
## Stack
- Expo SDK, Expo Router (file-based routing), TypeScript
- Zustand (state management), @tanstack/react-query
- Supabase (backend/auth), RevenueCat (IAP)
- expo-av (audio playback), expo-notifications
- react-native-google-mobile-ads (AdMob)
- react-native-reanimated (animations)

## Architecture
- /app — routes (tabs, modals, stacks)
- /src/stores — Zustand stores (playerStore, authStore)
- /src/services — API calls, Supabase client, RevenueCat
- /src/components — reusable UI components
- /src/data — static book data, categories
- /src/types — TypeScript interfaces

## Rules
- Functional components only, no class components
- Zustand stores: minimal state, derived values via selectors
- Audio: always cleanup sound instances on unmount/switch
- Navigation: use expo-router Link/useRouter, never react-navigation directly
- Styles: StyleSheet.create at bottom of file, no inline objects
- Platform-specific: use Platform.select or .ios.tsx/.android.tsx
- No any types — strict TypeScript
- Imports: absolute from src/ (configured in tsconfig)
- Test with: `npx expo-doctor`, `tsc --noEmit`
- IAP: always verify receipt server-side before granting access
